{"tid":436143,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《鐵甲奇俠4》羅拔唐尼確認回歸 將於2020年上映！","createTime":"2017-10-15T02:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T10:26:13.000Z","uid":105567,"like":13,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"89f9a591d25a08628d64ce59af8c87612f1d8612","tid":436143,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"在漫威超級英雄宇宙中，鐵甲奇俠是最受影迷們歡迎的角色之一。時至今日距離《鐵甲奇俠3》電影2013年上映已有4年的時間，很多人都期待影片的續集能早日推出。不負眾望好消息來了，荷李活將拍《鐵甲奇俠4》，系列主演羅拔唐尼將會回歸，影片將於2020年上映，不過前後7年真空期確實有點長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170824/bkn-20170824061623463-0824_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170824%2Fbkn-20170824061623463-0824_00862_001.html&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c787c4a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170824/bkn-20170824061623463-0824_00862_001.html</a><br />\n　　早前在第三部結束後，因為小羅伯特唐尼開出的片酬過高，加上漫威不想繼續拍攝第四部的意願，《鐵甲奇俠4》險些夭折。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過近日有喜訊傳來，《鐵甲奇俠4》已經正式立項，而原本打算換掉主角的想法也被否決，羅拔唐尼確認回歸《鐵甲奇俠4》，而且黑寡婦也會在《鐵甲奇俠4》中有不小戲份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉，《鐵甲奇俠4》將於明年開拍，預計2020年播出，當然了，具體消息還得等官方消息公佈，不過只要羅拔唐尼回歸，憑藉個人的號召力，《鐵甲奇俠4》再破十億票房輕輕鬆鬆。<br />\n<br />\n　　《鐵甲奇俠4》演員表：<br />\n<br />\n　　羅拔唐尼，桂莉芙柏德露，當卓度，佳皮雅斯，施嘉莉祖安遜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3818/12125836745_d88be61200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm4.staticflickr.com%2F3818%2F12125836745_d88be61200.jpg&h=61686e14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cac3ab98c3b782f8c52ab742b68a05317e6f526","tid":436143,"uid":10819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1c59f3cecdf756b293ec89cf3be4136c6fee96","tid":436143,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"講extremis就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9ad4e5b2d5eb597ee0c04de3d923b13fad34ae","tid":436143,"uid":33821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"尋日明珠930 ultron age個post有巴打講左係假"},{"pid":"4b128df6b375cc0eb7ab070e8b1fcf0b7a897ef6","tid":436143,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"如果故事係講鐵甲俠既接班人都好"},{"pid":"bf0c1dab08309867ab271707f17a21cd77b3c702","tid":436143,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"滿大人出黎未？"},{"pid":"d0c449feeb5f707f823a4e8a86ca1cc2872732c9","tid":436143,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"D甲都炸哂仲有咩可以講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eef10d2a5696dbb1cb407b0fbb3b2038ca540a","tid":436143,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D甲都炸哂仲有咩可以講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n復仇者聯盟二之前都炸哂，要整新甲難唔到佢"},{"pid":"7491fae501869e2ebfe4936139d358fa99667beb","tid":436143,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D甲都炸哂仲有咩可以講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有錢 好快整得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d80b729aec2ff9ae72fb47bbb1b3cbd638897b","tid":436143,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"google iron man 4 都冇乜新聞"},{"pid":"382379551fde958b1861f0d0d09110561eeac143","tid":436143,"uid":861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"假架啵ching"},{"pid":"be2e89efb52ff031a18d3f9dd51e759d7161ee74","tid":436143,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"搵